"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-doc","name":"feishu-doc","description":"Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links.","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc/SKILL.md","baseDir":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc","origin":"top-level","path":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-drive","name":"feishu-drive","description":"Feishu cloud storage file management. Activate when user mentions cloud space, folders, drive.","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-drive/SKILL.md","baseDir":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-drive","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-drive","origin":"top-level","path":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-drive/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-fetch-doc","name":"feishu-fetch-doc","description":"获取飞书云文档内容。返回文档的 Markdown 内容，支持处理文档中的图片、文件和画板（需配合 feishu_doc_media 工具）。","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-fetch-doc/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-fetch-doc","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-fetch-doc","origin":"top-level","path":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-fetch-doc/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-im-read","name":"feishu-im-read","description":"飞书 IM 消息读取工具使用指南，覆盖会话消息获取、话题回复读取、跨会话消息搜索、图片/文件资源下载。\n\n**当以下情况时使用此 Skill**:\n(1) 需要获取群聊或单聊的历史消息\n(2) 需要读取话题（thread）内的回复消息\n(3) 需要跨会话搜索消息（按关键词、发送者、时间等条件）\n(4) 消息中包含图片、文件、音频、视频，需要下载\n(5) 用户提到\"聊天记录\"、\"消息\"、\"群里说了什么\"、\"话题回复\"、\"搜索消息\"、\"图片\"、\"文件下载\"\n(6) 需要按时间范围过滤消息、分页获取更多消息","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-im-read/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-im-read","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-im-read","origin":"top-level","path":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-im-read/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-perm","name":"feishu-perm","description":"Feishu permission management for documents and files. Activate when user mentions sharing, permissions, collaborators.","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-perm/SKILL.md","baseDir":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-perm","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-perm","origin":"top-level","path":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-perm/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-task","name":"feishu-task","description":"飞书任务管理工具,用于创建、查询、更新任务和清单。\n\n**当以下情况时使用此 Skill**:\n(1) 需要创建、查询、更新任务\n(2) 需要创建、管理任务清单\n(3) 需要查看任务列表或清单内的任务\n(4) 用户提到\"任务\"、\"待办\"、\"to-do\"、\"清单\"、\"task\"\n(5) 需要设置任务负责人、关注人、截止时间","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-task/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-task","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE